<item>
            <title>[PIG-304] Distinct fail if previous map plan is closed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-304</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Distinct will fail when the previous map plan is closed. For example, the following script fail:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a = load &apos;a&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
b = group a by $0;&lt;br/&gt;
c = foreach b generate $1;&lt;br/&gt;
d = distinct c;&lt;br/&gt;
dump d;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
